WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:04.000
ST-Firm presents.

00:04.000 --> 00:08.000
Jenga… jenga… Powered by SSOS.

00:08.000 --> 00:12.000
Learn. Build. Share. Empower.

00:12.000 --> 00:22.000
Ravine to the World! Twende pamoja!
29 active online members.

