00:43.000 --> 00:47.000
Sema SSOS. Sovereign intelligence.
Business continuity.

00:47.000 --> 00:49.550
Akädemie.

00:49.550 --> 00:50.300
Learn. Build. Share. Empower.

00:50.300 --> 00:53.300
Knowledge becomes engineering.
Engineering connects intelligence.

00:53.300 --> 00:56.500
Intelligence strengthens real operations.
Operations create real-world value.

00:56.500 --> 00:58.000
Value returns to people and builds the next generation.

00:58.000 --> 01:05.000
Taking Ravine to the World
and bringing the World to Eldama Ravine.

01:05.000 --> 01:10.000
Engineer Saigut Julius Kipkorir—AKA KingKunta.
